    <p>Freeway Mobile Tyres are your local locking wheel nut removal specialists in Dorset. If you’ve got a damaged wheel nut key or lost your socket, we can remove your lockers with our universal tools. And, best of all, we can perform this service at your location for no extra cost. So if you’re stuck at home or the roadside, we can come to you!</p>
